{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stdDeviation","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stdDeviation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>stdDeviation</code> 属性定义了模糊操作的标准差。如果列出两个 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/SVG/Content_type#Number\">&lt;number&gt;</a>，第一个数字表示沿着 x 轴的标准差值，第二个值表示沿着 y 轴的标准差值。如果只出现一个数字，那个值就表示在 x 轴和 y 轴上有着相同的标准差。</p>\n\n<p>负值是不允许的。设为零即禁用了已有滤镜的原本效果（比如，结果是滤镜输入图像）。如果 <code>stdDeviation</code> 在 x 轴和 y 轴上只有一个为 0，那么模糊效果就只会应用于非 0 的那个方向。</p>\n\n<p>如果此属性没被定义，就与标准差值被定义为 0 的效果一样。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number-optional-number\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/SVG/Content_type#Number-optional-number\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feGaussianBlurStdDeviationAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n  <dt id=\"number-optional-number_2\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A pair of &lt;number&gt;s, where the second &lt;number&gt; is optional.</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number-optional-number ::= number\n                            | number, number\n</pre>\n    <p>In the SVG DOM, a &lt;number-optional-number&gt; is represented using a pair of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedInteger\"><code>SVGAnimatedInteger</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedNumber\"><code>SVGAnimatedNumber</code></a> objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下的元素可以使用 <code>stdDeviation</code> 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feGaussianBlur\"><code>&lt;feGaussianBlur&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stdDeviation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stddeviation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stddeviation/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stdDeviation","title":"stdDeviation"}],"pageTitle":"stdDeviation - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}